Package com.olap3.cubeexplorer.model

Class Qfset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.olap3.cubeexplorer.model.Qfset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Measurable<Qfset>, java.io.Serializable
    public class Qfset
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Measurable<Qfset>
    This is the cube query, it has lower expresion power than MDX but it can be translated into a star join and should be closed over the set of cuboids. This is based on Julien's original model for queries and query fragments but it has seen heavy changes. Deprecated methods are unpredictable and should be avoided.
    Author:
    Julien Aligon, Aleandre Chanson
    See Also:
